data.description: Location, location, location. Welcome home to this quaint cape code home located just minutes from the lakeshore.  This home offers three bedrooms, one and a half bathrooms, living room, eat in kitchen and a partially finished basement.  The backyard is completely fenced in and offers access to your two stall garage.   Don't miss out as this home wont last long!
